<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 dōu qū rǔ de rěn shòu guò wú qíng de pí biān dōu jiān nán de liú zhe lèi zǒu guò xīn suān
 dào le jīn tiān hái yào xiàng qián zhí dào jiàn zhǔ de nà yī tiān.
 dào dà jiē xiǎo xiàng qù zhǎo mí yáng wǒ men de dān zi xì zhe rén jiān de lěng nuǎn
 lǎo wēng hái tóng hé guǎi zhàng shēng yě bù yuàn luò zài hòu biān
 tiān bù zǎo lù bù yuǎn jūn wáng de xīn dōu yào gǎi biàn
 duō shǎo nián dài de yù yán dōu kuài yīng yàn wán.</lyrics>
<title>hái yào xiàng qián 迦南356</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
